I plan to gain a wordcloud first to search 250 tweets and take a first browse of the datasets I gathered. I will gather more tweets in the future and transfer it to several datasets in order to gain more comparison between platforms.

#Cleaning the text
twittertext1 = tm_map(twittertext1, content_transformer(tolower))
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(twittertext1, content_transformer(tolower)):
## transformation drops documents
twittertext1 = tm_map(twittertext1, removeNumbers)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(twittertext1, removeNumbers): transformation
## drops documents
twittertext1 = tm_map(twittertext1, stripWhitespace)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(twittertext1, stripWhitespace): transformation
## drops documents
#Build a term-document matrix
twittertm = TermDocumentMatrix(twittertext1)
m = as.matrix(twittertm)
v = sort(rowSums(m), 
         decreasing = TRUE)
d = data.frame(word = names(v),
               freq = v)
